# outOfDate

**Type Property**

A status value that indicates that the downloaded asset pack is out of date.

## Declaration

```swift
static let outOfDate: AssetPack.Status
```

## Discussion

The presence of this status value doesn’t necessarily imply that an update to the asset pack can be downloaded over the current network connection. Check for the presence of [doc://com.apple.backgroundassets/documentation/BackgroundAssets/AssetPack/Status/downloadAvailable] to determine whether an update can currently be downloaded.

## Updating assets

- **upToDate**: A status value that indicates that the downloaded asset pack is up to date.
- **obsolete**: A status value that indicates that the asset pack is no longer available to download.
- **updateAvailable**: A status value that indicates that an update to the asset pack is available to download.
